315335581.Title: Hamilton Beach 5.0 cu. ft. Residential Chest Freezer in Granite, Granite look
315335581.Description: This 5.0 cu. ft. capacity chest freezer has a compact foot print suitable for a variety of placement options. Yet, it's large enough to hold many of your frozen foods. It has a unique granite look finish that looks great with any decor.

311895691.Title: Magic Chef 7.0 cu. ft. Chest Freezer in White
311895691.Description: The Magic Chef 7.0 cu. ft. chest freezer will let you stock up on all your extra favorite frozen foods. It offers installation flexibility, and should ideally be placed in areas where the ambient temperature ranges from 32°F to 100°F for efficient operation. The external temperature control makes it easy and efficient to operate because you can make temperature adjustments without opening the lid. The sliding baskets make it easier to organize and access your frozen items. Its interior LED light allows for easy viewing. Recessed handle adds to its premium and sleek design. Interior Freezer temperature can range from 6° F to -8°F. Color: White.

316856885.Title: NewAir 6.7 cu. ft. Compact Chest Freezer in Black
316856885.Description: Whether you're looking to stockpile meals or just want to know you'll never run out of party snacks, the right chest freezer will help you stay prepared for anything the world throws at you. The NewAir 6.7 cu. ft. compact chest freezer provides everything you need to keep your family well fed. Digital temperature controls let you set the thermostat to your exact needs for grocery store staples or specialty items from hunting and fishing trips. Smart features like Fast Freeze Mode and a door alarm make this compact yet spacious chest freezer the perfect addition to any home. Color: Black.

309814622.Title: Danby 7.2 cu. ft. Chest Freezer in Black with 5-Year Warranty
309814622.Description: This dependable chest freezer by Danby is the perfect addition to any type of household or cottage. Your electricity bills will be noticeably reduced due to the efficient and smart foam-insulated cabinet and rounded lid. The easy-to-access front-mount mechanical thermostat allows you to easily and quickly program the unit to the desired temperature. There's more than enough storage room in this elegant appliance as this spacious unit offers 7.2 cu. ft. (204 l) of space without taking up too much room. This popular model comes with a convenient manual-defrost system and drain along with a strong vinyl-coated basket to separate and store your most popular foods. The interior liner is designed for easy cleaning and the freezer comes with a worry-free 5-years warranty on parts and labor along with convenient in-home service. Color: Black.
